    <div class="text-3xl py-3 font-bold">Software Engineer</div>
    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        Hi everyone, I'm Anh, or you can call me Harris. I'm a Computer Science
        student in VNUHCM - University of Science. I have a passion for
