        with. Currently I'm learning about Blockchain and Solidity, and I also
        looking for an internship in that field. Please let me know via
        messaging or email for me by phnanh.harris@gmail.com if you are looking
        for intern and feel interested in my curriculum vitae. I also have a
        Vietnamese personal blog at here. Browse it and you'll read many posts
        about some topics that interest me like technology, wine, and
        motorbikes. Starting to work while studying in university was an
        opportunity and a challenge for me in my career as a programmer. The
        first experiences on this road help me a lot in work and life, have more
        lessons and friends that are important in my career path later.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://twitter.com/manuelernestog" target="_blank">
        Let's connect!</a
      >
      <a
        href="https://github.com/manuelernestog/astro-modern-personal-website"
        target="_blank"
        class="btn btn-outline ml-5"
      >
        Get This template</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2">
      My last projects {"</>"}
